\v 28 Ivangy…õ unga aka imaa ikorha ak…õr…õ ha, m…Ēc…õ Ungw…õŐÉ h√£ aka isei ru ubok Unum aka atsuke abina kishoo ru uboknga, nggee Unum unga awu abina kishoo.
\p 
\v 29 Isok ra akpe iba ishingge, ab…Ēr…Ē umb…Ē aka asorhuwe umb…Ē ub…Ētisima ri itsi abika akpe, awuri ikorha aguse? Uba abika akpe asi √≠sokmb…Ē ra akpe, awu use utsu anera asorhu ub…Ētisima?
