\v 58 Nggee, umbi aze angw…õŐÉm…õn nu anapum…õn aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ aker. Niba neke ubin ug…Ēpukp…Ē umbi. Ub…õn ivang aka adzowe atsimbi kishoo ri itser Uteijee, ubinkutsu umbi ahw…õngmbi ayetnummbi ru Uteijee asi √≠weke ib…õm.
\c 16
\s1 IzŇ©w√£ iyiki iyike abika ad…Ēsa
