\v 19 Ikik…Ēng abika ad…Ēsa ra abń© Uasiya aghwe umbi. Uakirha nu Ubiriskirha aghwe umbi akarh√£rh√£ ri itsok Uteijee, nu abika ad…Ēsa aki ik…Ēng ri iyamb…Ē.
\v 20 Kishoo angw…õŐÉm…õn nu anapum…õn nggimi aghwe umbi. √Äka aghwe ad…Ēka nggu ighwe ibibema.
